Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:32.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,420)}我有预感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.45,0:01:35.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,420)}多彩的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.93,0:01:38.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,420)}品尝、惊讶
